# Bill Scanner (optional)
# Without this key the app works fully — only the PDF bill upload feature is disabled.
#
# To enable bill scanning:
# 1. Get an API key from https://console.anthropic.com
# 2. Copy this file to .env.local  (never commit .env.local — it's in .gitignore)
# 3. Set your key below
# 4. Run: npm run dev
#
# NOTE: Direct browser → Anthropic calls require the
# "anthropic-dangerous-direct-browser-access" header (set automatically when key is present).
# For production use, a backend proxy is recommended so the key stays off the client.
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Address Geocoding — Geoapify (required for address lookup & autocomplete)
# Sign up free at https://www.geoapify.com (3,000 requests/day free tier)
# Create a project, generate two API keys, and add domain restriction:
#   Allowed origin: https://pandafs23.github.io
VITE_GEOAPIFY_KEY=
VITE_GEOAPIFY_AUTOCOMPLETE_KEY=
